  "texts": [
    "Strategies for Extracting Action Knowledge.",
    "Given the diverse action knowledge involved in various tasks, fully manual construction is both time-consuming and labor-intensive.",
    "To overcome this, we leverage GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023), known for its strong performance on such tasks (Liu et al., 2023a; Ouyang and Li, 2023), for initial construction.",
    "Our two-stage process starts with domain experts providing task knowledge to the LLM, which generates a preliminary list of actions and rules.",
    "Since the initial output often includes redundancy, human experts then filter and refine this list."
  ],
